<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - CRA Managed upped to buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - CRA Managed upped to buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Bear Stearns has raised its rating for CRA Managed Care Inc to buy from attractive based on the stock's price, a source at the brokerage said on Monday.</p>
<p>-- Shares in the Boston workers compensation cost-containment company closed on Friday at 39-3/4.</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street desk (212) 859-1730))</p>
